text: Patricija Šulin (25 November 1965 – 2 November 2021) was a Slovenian politician. A member of the Slovenian Democratic Party and the European People's Party Group, she served in the European Parliament from 2014 to 2019 and in the National Assembly of Slovenia from 2012 to 2013. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:2021 deaths Category:MEPs for Slovenia
title: Patricija Šulin
